{"tid":1285223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡太引述胡國興談示威 ：梗係企喺年青人一邊！","createTime":"2019-07-04T13:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T02:59:47.000Z","uid":2617,"like":804,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"2207d6fb68709622f8d4c16b6f668232d1af7adb","tid":1285223,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"2017年參選特首選舉落敗的73歲退休法官胡國興正在瑪麗醫院深切治療部接受治療，胡國興太太與兒子及其太太晚上到瑪麗醫院探訪。胡太指，胡官早前整傷腰骨，惟其後遭細菌入侵，結果造成腰骨發炎，胡官已入住醫院十日，現時情況穩定，預料這一、兩天會離開深切治療部。<br />\n<br />\n近日反《逃犯條例》修訂運動引發巨大政治風暴 ，胡太稱，胡官非常留意社會發生的新聞，惟她引述胡官稱自己「不在其位、不謀其政」，強調他只是關心事件。<br />\n<br />\n對於近日發生的示威活動，胡太稱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「佢梗係企喺年青人一邊啦」，亦認為「有啲嘢政府應該要做」</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n胡太表示，胡官現時「食到嘢、講到嘢」，預料一、兩日後離開深切治療部。"},{"pid":"53a52b147630e828e2acc9e5e7db46345739f7da","tid":1285223,"uid":200758,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a10e943c21aa2badcac9238145d10b6dee2ff498","tid":1285223,"uid":75664,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"胡官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a090db136bb132fb180f33a1648bb743f1479a51","tid":1285223,"uid":212626,"like":163,"dislike":0,"score":163,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"法律界有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af8189b80d386ac830cd5a70727d3f6c3ebd20c","tid":1285223,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac1398ca550da5b20de090c65a6fc90b02b6ac0","tid":1285223,"uid":2617,"like":311,"dislike":4,"score":307,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"胡官=長者<br />\n其他老屎忽=廢老<