me":"2019-07-04T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"希望身體無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30675ce2df77c8dc2030d66d147f8de72854ef8f","tid":1285223,"uid":16506,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"發夢見到胡生話應該成立獨立委員會，因為政府不嬲係咁做。"},{"pid":"3e26da84e8104682a50423fafc01bde97cdc35ae","tid":1285223,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"胡官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09259fff278088ad76d5003beb0df1cc0528012a","tid":1285223,"uid":2617,"like":180,"dislike":0,"score":180,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:23:48.000Z","msg":"回帶：<br />\n<br />\n胡官2017年感言<br />\n<br />\n我參選第一個階段的目的係ABC，已經做到。第二階段要睇以後，我建議重啟政改、22條立法、全民退保，如果最終有民意支持落實，我就超額完成。<br />\n<br />\n最後我有心底說話，特別想同各位年青朋友講。記者朋友好鍾意問我：有無後悔，有無失望，覺唔覺得唔公平？我相信呢啲問題，反映好多香港人而家嘅受壓抑嘅心理狀況。<br />\n<br />\n我希望我呢個71歲香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「不含糊、不閃避」、「有話直講，勇往直前」</span></span>嘅態度，多多少少可以為社會作出積極嘅示範作用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2ec706ac1c03e12f4615cda8f903a692f02589","tid":1285223,"uid":217506,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安，認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無野講 我要見律師 唔好兇我 我投訴你"},{"pid":"3e29c73c7213c3540439c1d1129656ee4c0a8265","tid":1285223,"uid":2617,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"30675ce2df77c8dc2030d66d147f8de72854ef8f","tid":1285223,"uid":16506,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"發夢見到胡生話應該成立獨立委員會，因為政府不嬲係咁做。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"根本就係天經地義<br />\n連呢樣都唔敢做<br />\n驚死查到自己同警狗有嚴重缺失<br />\n佢都on99<br />\n呢樣根本唔駛查都知<